OL,3,CSouthampton await their fate with
OL,4,C'Spygate' hearing result expected
OL,6,FThe independent commission hearing on
OL,7,F'Spygate' is due to take place on
OL,8,FTuesday as everyone connected to
OL,9,FSouthampton, Middlesbrough and Hull
OL,10,Fawaits clarity on the Championship
OL,11,Fplay-off final.
OL,13,FSaints were charged with a breach of
OL,14,FEFL regulations 10 days ago, having
OL,15,Fbeen reported for allegedly spying on
OL,16,Fa Boro training session at their
OL,17,FRockcliffe Park base, ahead of the
OL,18,Ffirst leg of their semi-final
OL,19,Fencounter.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
