OL,3,CSouthampton await their fate with
OL,4,C'Spygate' hearing result expected
OL,6,FTonda Eckert's side survived an early
OL,7,Fonslaught to draw 0-0 at the Riverside
OL,8,FStadium and won the return fixture 2-1
OL,9,Fafter extra-time, setting up a play-
OL,10,Foff final between Southampton and
OL,11,Fsurprise package Hull.
OL,13,FBut Middlesbrough have publicly
OL,14,Fdemanded that the Hampshire club are
OL,15,Fprevented from playing in the Wembley
OL,16,Fshowpiece, which is scheduled for
OL,17,F4.30pm on Saturday, due to their
OL,18,Fconduct.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
