OL,3,CSouthampton await their fate with
OL,4,C'Spygate' hearing result expected
OL,6,FThe Press Association understands the
OL,7,Findependent commission will meet to
OL,8,Frule on the matter today, but the
OL,9,Fpotential for an appeal creates
OL,10,Funcertainty for all three clubs, their
OL,11,Ffans and stakeholders.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
