OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779260760
OL,3,CSouthampton await their fate with
OL,4,C'Spygate' hearing result expected
OL,6,FSouthampton and Hull have both been
OL,7,Fselling tickets since Friday, but the
OL,8,FEFL warned the previous day it had "a
OL,9,Fnumber of contingency plans" in place
OL,10,Fdepending on the outcome of
OL,11,Fproceedings.
OL,13,FWhile the governing body plans for a
OL,14,FMay 23 final, it admitted: "Supporters
OL,15,Fshould, however, be aware that the
OL,16,Foutcome of the disciplinary
OL,17,Fproceedings may yet result in changes
OL,18,Fto the fixture."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
