OL,3,CSouthampton await their fate with
OL,4,C'Spygate' hearing result expected
OL,6,FSaints players resumed training on
OL,7,FSunday ahead of the scheduled Wembley
OL,8,Fshowpiece following a break, while the
OL,9,FTigers are attempting to stay focused
OL,10,Fon a Saturday clash against the south
OL,11,Fcoast club.
OL,13,FSergej Jakirovic's City trained last
OL,14,FThursday and Friday following their
OL,15,Fimpressive semi-final victory at third-
OL,16,Fplaced Millwall, before returning to
OL,17,Ftheir Cottingham base on Monday
OL,18,Ffollowing a weekend off.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
